<div id="community-vibe">
    <h2 class="sect-title">Community Vibe in Elbow Park</h2>
    <div class="col-grid-2">
        <div>
            <p class="par-lg">As a family oriented area, Elbow Park offers sports for children to young adults. </p>
            <p class="par-lg">Community soccer is available during the spring and summer months. Hockey is also available via Glenlake Hockey.</p>
            <p class="par-lg">Stanley Park and River Park border the community in the Elbow River valley, an excellent location for picnics, barbeques and walks.</p>
            <p class="par-lg">There is also an off-leash dog park overlooking the valley, making it ideal for dog owners.</p>
            <p class="par-lg">4th Street in Mission is located north along Elbow Drive. 4th street is home to a variety of restaurants, shops and other services. 17th Avenue is also located a close distance, with that and 4th making up a large entertainment area of Calgary, with a well-known nightlife and shopping scene.</p>


            <p class="par-lg">The Calgary Board of Education, which has an elementary and junior high in the area,
                services Elbow Parkâ€™s education, with several high schools being located in neighbouring communities.
            </p>
        </div>
